title: Deposit drain from smaller banks into financial giants like JPMorgan Chase has slowed, sources say
description: Uncertainty caused by the collapse of Silicon Valley Bank this month triggered outflows and plunging share prices at peers including First Republic and PacWest.

title: 31-year-old used her $1,200 stimulus check to start a 'cash stuffing' business—it's on track to bring in $1 million this year
description: Jasmine Taylor went viral on TikTok using a budget method called "cash stuffing." She turned it into a business that's on track to make $1 million this year.

title: The market's initial reaction to a Fed rate hike is 'almost always a head fake,' Jim Cramer says
description: CNBC's Jim Cramer said Friday that the initial market sell-off prompted by the Fed rate hike may point to a reversal in the coming months, based on past data.
